{"tid":1001013,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"法國版《城市獵人》真人電影預告","createTime":"2019-01-29T23:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:25:37.000Z","uid":64191,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8232884d811ea19ae6c676dcad0586e6a11eb0a0","tid":1001013,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T23:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GbxYYZrQf-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGbxYYZrQf-c&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=1222af4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GbxYYZrQf-c</a><br />\n<br />\n由索尼影業所發行的法國真人版電影《城市獵人：邱比特香水（Nicky Larson et le Parfum de Cupidon）預定今（2019）年 2 月 6 日將在法國上映，而片商威望國際（CatchPlay）近日也釋出了中文版的宣傳影片，電影目前預計將於 5 月 17 日在台上映。<br />\n<br />\n唔知香港會唔會上呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/09/86bf9dacb9a0c6f66f420787b413t155.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F09%2F86bf9dacb9a0c6f66f420787b413t155.JPG&h=473c98ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4383d19bf3c17b518f938923664f58498fdecab5","tid":1001013,"uid":5073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:48:04.000Z","msg":"有d期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3327d4abaa67d459b14d77f6a03da95cea5d5a2","tid":1001013,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"但香港好大機會只係上日本動畫版"},{"pid":"913a6c48ddc6c080c7577d52a7c8a15ee8b192c1","tid":1001013,"uid":33104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"都係周文健最似"},{"pid":"cf28f62174d27662e714ad7c0d6475f2273fe5e8","tid":1001013,"uid":217162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e287b94e3b97295cd0b0073b814eb520708e471","tid":1001013